      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/25/422",
      "text": [
        " ثَلاَثَةِ أَثْوَابٍ بِغَيْرِ قَمِيصٍ قَالَ «لاَ بَأْسَ بِذَلِكَ وَ اَلْقَمِيصُ أَحَبُّ إِلَيَّ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.422 - Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) was asked about a man who dies and whether he can be shrouded in three garments without a shirt (Qamis).\nImam (as) said: \"There is no problem with that, but having a shirt is more preferred to me.\""
        ]
      }
    },
